name: Name of the API
description: Description of the API - please make as detailed as possible, as this is the primary source for the search function
documentation: Documentation link - should include URL to publicly accessible documentation
maintainer: Should include a non-individual (team) email address for users to be able to  contact about the API, for support and to begin data-sharing agreements
provider: Organisation or Governmemt Department responsible for producing the API
areaServed: Geographic area covered by the API
startDate: When the API comes into service
alternateName: Acronym or alternate name for the provider organisation
provider url: Canonical URL for the responsible department
